description: This file defines a React component named DashboardLayout, which serves as a layout wrapper for dashboard pages in a React application. It imports utility components from Material UI and custom components like SideNav and TopBar to construct a flexible, responsive layout with a side navigation panel and a top bar.

methods.name: DashboardLayout
methods.description: A React functional component that arranges a page's layout with a side navigation and top bar, wrapping children content within styled Box components.
